            <h3>1</h3>
            <img src="images/steak.jpg">
            <h4> Steak</h4>
            <p>Steak is a thick, tender slice of beef, usually cut from premium parts of the cow. It is typically grilled, pan-seared, or broiled to various levels of doneness, from rare to well-done.</p>
        </div>
        
        
        <div class="card">
            <h3> 2</h3>
            <img src="images/pasta.jpg">
            <h4> Pasta</h4>
            <p>A staple Italian dish made from flour and water, shaped into noodles of various forms like spaghetti, macaroni, or fettuccine. It is often served with tomato-based sauces, creamy Alfredo, or meaty Bolognese.</p>
        </div>
        
        
        <div class="card">
            <h3>3</h3>
            <img src="images/sushi.jpg">
            <h4> Sushi</h4>
            <p>A Japanese delicacy made with vinegared rice, many kinds of raw or cooked seafood, vegetables, and seaweed.</p>
        </div>
        
        
        <div class="card">
            <h3>4</h3>
            <img src="images/ramen.jpg">
            <h4> Ramen</h4>
            <p>A comforting Japanese noodle soup made with wheat noodles served in a savory broth made from various ingredients. It is commonly topped with sliced pork, boiled eggs, seaweed, and garnished with green onions.</p>
        </div>
        
        
        <div class="card">
            <h3>5</h3>
            <img src="images/tacos.jpg">
            <h4> Birria Tacos</h4>
            <p>Birria tacos are a flavorful Mexican dish made with slow-cooked, marinated beef that is shredded and put into corn tortillas. The tacos are then dipped in the rich, spicy birria broth before being grilled.</p>
        </div>
        
        
        <div class="card">
            <h3>6</h3>
            <img src="images/friedchicken.jpg">
            <h4> Fried chicken</h4>
            <p>Fried chicken is a crispy, golden-brown dish made by coating chicken pieces in seasoned flour or batter and deep-frying them until crunchy on the outside and juicy on the inside.</p>
        </div>
        
        
        <div class="card">
            <h3>7</h3>
            <img src="images/burger.jpg">
            <h4> Cheeseburger</h4>
            <p>A popular American fast food consisting of a grilled beef patty placed inside of a soft bun, often topped with lettuce, tomato, cheese, pickles, onions, and condiments like ketchup, mustard, and mayonnaise.</p>
        </div>
       

        <div class="card">
            <h3>8</h3>
            <img src="images/dimsum.jpg">
            <h4> Dimsum</h4>
            <p>A collection of small dishes, typically served in bamboo steamers. These dishes include dumplings, buns, rolls, and pastries filled with shrimp, pork, vegetables, or sweet custards.</p>
        </div>
        

        <div class="card">
            <h3>9</h3>
            <img src="images/pizzaparty.jpg">
            <h4> Pizza</h4>
            <p>A classic Italian dish consisting of a round, flat dough topped with tomato sauce, cheese, and various toppings such as pepperoni, mushrooms, or vegetables. It is baked in an oven until crispy and melted.</p>
        </div>
        

        <div class="card">
            <h3>10</h3>
            <img src="images/icecreamy.jpg">
            <h4> Ice cream</h4>
            <p>Ice cream is a creamy, frozen dessert made from dairy, sugar, and flavorings like vanilla, chocolate, or fruit.</p>
